'''登頓'''（{{lang en|'''Denton'''}}）是[[美國|美國]][[馬里蘭州|馬里蘭州]][[加羅林縣_(馬里蘭州)|加羅林縣]]的縣治。{{GR|6}}根據[[2010年美國人口普查|2010年人口普查]]，本鎮共有人口4,418人。<ref>[http://www2.census.gov/census_2010/01-Redistricting_File--PL_94-171/California/ "2010 Census P.L. 94-171 Summary File Data"] {{Wayback|url=http://www2.census.gov/census_2010/01-Redistricting_File--PL_94-171/California/ |date=20130807061126 }}. United States Census Bureau.</ref>

==歷史==
本鎮於1781年成立<ref name="#1"/>，取名末任馬里蘭殖民地統治者自[[羅伯特·伊登|羅伯特·伊登]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.epodunk.com/cgi-bin/genInfo.php?locIndex=2536|title=Profile for Denton, Maryland, MD|publisher=ePodunk|accessdate=August 24, 2012|archive-date=2019-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190514195914/http://epodunk.com/cgi-bin/genInfo.php?locIndex=2536|dead-url=no}}</ref>本鎮於1802註冊成立。<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.city-data.com/city/Denton-Maryland.html|title= Denton, Maryland|publisher= City-Data.com|accessdate= August 24, 2012|archive-date= 2020-07-16|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200716105042/http://www.city-data.com/city/Denton-Maryland.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>

==地理==
